<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="betray-vt">betray <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'treɪ/    美 /bɪ'treɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>出卖；背叛；泄漏；暴露：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I feel betrayed by my friend, Hannah.
我感觉自己被朋友汉纳出卖了。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>betray themselves</strong> every time they open their mouths. 
他们一张嘴就会露出马脚。</p><footer>人教⑧ – 4</footer></div></div>